Paper: hep-th/9803024

Date: 1998-03-03

Title: Parafermionic Representation of the Affine $sl(2/1)$ Algebra at

Fractional LevelAuthors: P. Bowcock, M. Hayes, A. Taormina

Comments: 5 pages, Latex 2e

Journal-ref: Phys.Lett. B468 (1999) 239-243

The four fermionic currents of the affine superalgebra $sl(2/1)$ atfractional level $k=1/u-1$, u positive integer, are shown to be realised interms of a free scalar field, an $sl(2)$ doublet field and a primary field ofthe parafermionic algebra $Z_{u-1}$.